1.  Download the Vector `.deb` package

    <Tabs
      className="mini"
      defaultValue="latest"
      values={[
        { label: 'Latest (<%= metadata.latest_version %>)', value: 'latest'},
        { label: 'Nightly', value: 'nightly'},
      ]}>

    <TabItem value="latest">

    ```bash
    curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -O <%= metadata.links.fetch("urls.vector_downloads.#{metadata.latest_version}/#{deb_name}") %> 
    ```

    </TabItem>
    <TabItem value="nightly">

    ```bash
    curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -O <%= metadata.links.fetch("urls.vector_downloads.nightly/latest/#{deb_name}") %>
    ```

    </TabItem>
    </Tabs>

2.  Install the downloaded package

    ```bash
    sudo dpkg -i <%= deb_name %>
    ```

3.  Start Vector

    ```bash
    sudo systemctl start vector
    ```
